lead_paragraph: Mariya Moore scored 22 points, Asia Durr added 21 and No. 13 Louisville rolled to a 78-60 win over North Carolina on Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: No. 13 Louisville Women Overtake North Carolina 78-60
